estformer-Yeezy-employee-lawsuit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestformer-Yeezy-employee-lawsuit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestformer-Yeezy-employee-lawsuit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestformer-Yeezy-employee-lawsuit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestformer-Yeezy-employee-lawsuit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）</a>解决了他在他的唐达学院（Donda Academy）的老师面临的诉讼，这是他们计划去审判的一个月。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/kanye-west-white-lives-matter-unforgivable-opinion-3323984"><b>凭借他的“白人生命问题”的特技，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）终于达到了没有回报的地步？</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这位说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-rejects-former-slave-name-and-demands-to-be-called-ye-from-now-on-3609117">已将自己的名字改名为Ye</a> ，他同意与学校的前助理校长以赛亚草地和老师Cecilia Hailey，Chekarey Byers和Timanii Meeks进行有条件的和解，他们在2023年均在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/kanye-west-settles-donda-academy-lawsuits-ahead-of-trial-1235291205/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>2023</em></a>年向西方起诉。</p><p>案件最初定于4月进行审判，但韦斯特未能审理诉讼，他的律师要求2024年8月退出案件，声称说唱歌手已解雇了他并拒绝支付费用。</p><p>此后，据报道，由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">社交媒体上有很多争议的咆哮，</a>韦斯特一直无法找到新的法律代表。</p><p>韦斯特将不得不在45天内履行协议的结束，教师将向洛杉矶高等法院提交解雇请求。</p><p> <em>NME</em>已联系West的代表发表评论。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-opens-new-private-school-donda-academy-3311906">韦斯特于2022年开设了基于学费的基督教学校</a>。该学校以他已故的母亲的名字命名，旨在“使学生成为下一代领导者”，该网站上说，每天的时间表包括“完整的学校崇拜，语言艺术，数学和科学，午餐和休息，核心课程，包括世界语言，视觉艺术，电影，合唱团和跑酷等丰富课程”。</p><p>每年费用为15,000美元（约13,000英镑），尽管如当时网站的录取页面上所述，“欢迎每个人都适用，无论财务状况如何。经济援助和奖学金适用于资格的学生”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3842500" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3842500" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3842500" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3842500" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特。学分：爱德华·伯特洛（Edward Berthelot）/GC图像</figcaption></figure><p>在韦斯特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanyes-twitter-and-instagram-accounts-locked-after-antisemitic-posts-3325446">在2022年10月首次臭名昭著的反犹太蒂拉德（Tirade）</a>之后，这很快就陷入了争议。在其他许多古怪的说法中，他告诉他需要<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-tells-jewish-people-to-forgive-hitler-compares-porn-to-the-holocaust-3361860">“原谅希特勒”</a>为大屠杀而“原谅希特勒”  - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-apologises-jewish-community-antisemitic-comments-3563267">他在2023年为回来道歉</a>。在讲话之后，各个家庭开始将孩子从学校里拉出来。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-threatened-to-cage-donda-academy-students-new-lawsuit-claims-3612681">去年由西部的前雇员特雷弗·菲利普斯（Trevor Phillips）提起了另一项诉讼</a>。在此案中，他指责西部有许多爆炸性指控，包括口头虐待，威胁身体暴力并将自己与希特勒进行比较。</p><p>正如包括<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/kanye-west-donda-academy-lawsuit-kids-cages-shave-heads-rcna145966" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NBC新闻</em></a>， <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/kanye-west-lawsuit-donda-school-1234997814/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石</em></a>和<a href="https://consequence.net/2024/04/kanye-west-donda-academy-cage-students/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>后果</em></a>在内的各种媒体所强调的那样，菲利普斯声称韦斯特告诉学生，他想剃光头并将其锁在笼子里。他还声称说唱歌手经常称赞希特勒，甚至一次将自己与纳粹领导人进行了比较。</p><p> 2月，托马斯·朗（Thomas Long）法官命令韦斯特（West）支付2,560美元的罚款，并在4月30日不迟于4月30日待命，但由于韦斯特（West）的律师爱德华多·马托雷尔（Eduardo Martorell）表示，他无法保证与说唱歌手的交流，因此无法确定约会。 “我的客户不是那么合理。正如<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/kanye-west-sanctions-lawsuit-antisemitic-tirades-1235274166/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队</em></a>报道的那样，他说。</p><p>海莉（Hailey）和拜尔斯（Byers）是2023年首位诉讼的前唐纳学院（Donda Academy）的工作人员，声称学生在学习中“至少落后两年”。同时，米克斯（Meeks）指责西部禁止填字游戏和着色表，禁止使用硬椅使用，并坚持在一楼举行所有班级，因为他“据说害怕楼梯”。</p><p>所有的老师都声称，当他们告诉学校的领导他们的担忧时，他们被不公平地解雇了。 </p><figure id="attachment_3840227" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3840227" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3840227" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5.jpg" alt="坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）参加了第67届年度格莱美奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3840227" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）参加了第67届年度格莱美奖。学分：录音学院的Matt Winkelmeyer/Getty Image</figcaption></figure><p>近几个月来，韦斯特（West）因在他的网站上出售<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">胸部上有大巨大的swastika标志的白色T恤而</a>受到抨击，这可能是对“ Heil Hitler” Chant的参考。</p><p>该网站<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">后来被Shopify取消</a>，尽管在线零售商后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-says-kanye-wests-site-was-removed-over-fraud-potential-not-swastika-t-shirt-3837621">表示，由于欺诈的可能性，艺术家的网站被取消了 - 不是因为它出售了Swastika T恤</a>。 Shopify确实谴责了该物品，称其为“卑鄙，令人作呕和不可原谅”。</p><p>韦斯特然后去X（以前是Twitter）说他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-had-swastika-t-shirt-idea-for-over-eight-years-3838835">有“八年多”的T恤的想法</a>。 It came alongside a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">string of highly controversial posts</a> which saw him <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">rescind his apology to the Jewish community for his past anti-Semitic remarks</a> , and go on to declare himself “a Nazi” and write: “I love Hitler”, as well as praise billionaire and X owner <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">Elon Musk</a> as “the most lit person that [has] ever been on Twitter”, following <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">the latter&#39;s accusations of Nazism at Donald Trump&#39;s presidential inauguration</a> .</p><p>然后，这位备受争议的说唱歌手似乎回避了他先前的评论， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-has-come-to-the-realisation-that-hes-not-a-nazi-a